data.description: Nice Duplex conveniently located in Haddon Township ready for new owner or investor to add their personal touch. Corner property. 1 bedroom / 1 bath on 2nd floor. 2 bed / 1 bath on 1st floor.  1st Floor apartment bathroom fully remodel in 2022.  Property fully rented.  Garage also rented. Separate heat/hot water and electric. Good cash flowing rental property 1st Floor 2 bed unit is $1090 (typically renting in area for $1,800 to $2,000)  and is a Month-to-Month lease. 2nd Floor 1 Bed unit is $860  (Typically renting in area for $1,000 to $1,200) lease ending December. Two car garage rent is $150 and is Month to month.  Total: $2100/ month. This won’t last long, so be sure to make your appointment today!
